\begin{abstract}
In this paper, it is shown that 
the set consisting of stable convex integrands $S^n\to \mathbb{R}_+$ is 
open and dense in the set consisting of $C^\infty$ convex integrands 
with respect to Whitney $C^\infty$ topology.    
Moreover, an application of the proof of this result is also shown.   
 \end{abstract}


